# ============================================
# SUPABASE DATABASE CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# Direct Connection (Required for NextAuth database sessions)
# Get from: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → Database → Connection String → Prisma tab
# Copy this file to `apps/web/.env.local` for local app runtime secrets.
# Keep `apps/web/.env` minimal with `DATABASE_URL` only so Prisma CLI
# commands continue to work locally.

